  "body": "when we received an invalid stats history request, we can choose two ways to handle this request:\r\n1. treat it as an no indexes request in which we will return top ones block histories(but we need to ensure this request cannot block readLoop)\r\n2. just ignore it \r\n\r\nSo, if we want to treat it as an no indexes request(which is what we are doing now):\r\nhttps://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/blob/46698d79310ab1c12089f4bc2c13ac2f136128da/ethstats/ethstats.go#L323\r\nWe should ensure safety of this blocking channel as what we are doing when handle normal requests:\r\nhttps://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/blob/46698d79310ab1c12089f4bc2c13ac2f136128da/ethstats/ethstats.go#L341-L345",
